# Docker build context is the monorepo root for both apps (see
# app/notes/go/docker-compose.yml and app/blog/docker-compose.yml).
# Keep the build context lean and reproducible.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.astro
**/.unlighthouse
**/screenshots
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
**/*.log
.env
.env.*
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/README.md
# Regenerated by `pagefind` during the build; never ship the dev copy.
**/public/pagefind
